HEADWORD: Chloranil
<hw>Chlor`an"il</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Chlor</ets>ine + <ets>anil</ets>ine.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A yellow crystalline substance,
<chform>C6Cl4.O2</chform>, regarded as a derivative of quinone, obtained
by the action of chlorine on certain benzene derivatives, as
aniline.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chlorate</ent>⟦br⟧
